{
  "meta": {
    "schemaVersion": "1.0.0",
    "name": "day-end",
    "description": "End of day — advance day counter, update game stage, check phone unlocks",
    "inputs": [],
    "outputs": [
      {
        "name": "result",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "data": {
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "prompt-build",
        "type": "PromptBuild",
        "label": "Stage check prompt",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "object",
            "defaultValue": {}
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "messages",
            "type": "ChatMessage[]"
          },
          {
            "name": "text",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "estimatedTokens",
            "type": "number"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "defaultRole": "system",
          "fragments": [
            {
              "type": "base",
              "id": "role",
              "content": "根据当前天数确定游戏阶段和手机解锁状态。纯逻辑判断，不需要叙事。\n\n重要：你必须将day值+1后返回。例如当前day=5，你应返回day=6。\n\n游戏阶段规则（用+1后的day判断）：\n- Day 1-9: adaptation\n- Day 10-18: investigation\n- Day 19-27: deepening\n- Day 28-36: endgame\n\n手机解锁规则（用+1后的day判断）：\n- Day 2+: phoneUnlocked_social = true\n- Day 4+: phoneUnlocked_dm = true\n- Day 7+: phoneUnlocked_forum = true\n- Day 14+: phoneUnlocked_anon = true\n\n结局轴判定（仅在day+1>36时计算）：\n- 真相深度轴：所有线≤1=surface, 任一线≥3=middle, 两线≥3且convergenceDiscovered=deep\n- 人际影响轴：根据NPC命运统计（拯救≥4=guardian, 拯救2-3+深渊1-2=catalyst, 旁观≥4=bystander, 深渊≥3=destroyer）\n\n输出JSON：\n{\n  \"stateChanges\": {\n    \"day\": 当前day+1的值,\n    \"gameStage\": \"阶段名\",\n    \"phoneUnlocked_social\": true/false,\n    \"phoneUnlocked_dm\": true/false,\n    \"phoneUnlocked_forum\": true/false,\n    \"phoneUnlocked_anon\": true/false,\n    \"gameOver\": true（仅day+1>36时）,\n    \"endingTruthAxis\": \"仅day+1>36\",\n    \"endingImpactAxis\": \"仅day+1>36\"\n  }\n}",
              "role": "system"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "day",
              "source": "state.day",
              "label": "当前天数（已+1后的值）"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "lineA",
              "source": "state.lineA_depth",
              "label": "Line A深度"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "lineB",
              "source": "state.lineB_depth",
              "label": "Line B深度"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "lineC",
              "source": "state.lineC_depth",
              "label": "Line C深度"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "convergence",
              "source": "state.convergenceDiscovered",
              "label": "汇聚已发现"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "npcFates",
              "source": "state.npcFates",
              "label": "NPC命运"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "message",
        "type": "Message",
        "label": "Assemble",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "system",
            "type": "ChatMessage[]"
          },
          {
            "name": "user",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "messages",
            "type": "ChatMessage[]"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "historyKey": "history",
          "maxHistoryMessages": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "generate",
        "type": "GenerateText",
        "label": "Calculate stage",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "messages",
            "type": "ChatMessage[]"
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "text",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "usage",
            "type": "object"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "responseFormat": "json",
          "temperature": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "json-parse",
        "type": "JSONParse",
        "label": "Parse",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "text",
            "type": "string",
            "required": true
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "object"
          },
          {
            "name": "success",
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          {
            "name": "error",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "extractFromCodeBlock": true,
          "fixCommonErrors": true,
          "fixTruncated": true
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "apply-state",
        "type": "ApplyState",
        "label": "Apply stage",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "changes",
            "type": "object",
            "required": true
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "applied",
            "type": "array"
          },
          {
            "name": "success",
            "type": "boolean"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "path": "stateChanges",
          "allowedKeys": [
            "day",
            "gameStage",
            "gameOver",
            "phoneUnlocked_social",
            "phoneUnlocked_dm",
            "phoneUnlocked_forum",
            "phoneUnlocked_anon",
            "endingTruthAxis",
            "endingImpactAxis"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "signal-out",
        "type": "SignalOut",
        "label": "Output",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "channel": "result"
        }
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "source": "prompt-build",
        "sourceHandle": "messages",
        "target": "message",
        "targetHandle": "system"
      },
      {
        "source": "message",
        "sourceHandle": "messages",
        "target": "generate",
        "targetHandle": "messages"
      },
      {
        "source": "generate",
        "sourceHandle": "text",
        "target": "json-parse",
        "targetHandle": "text"
      },
      {
        "source": "generate",
        "sourceHandle": "text",
        "target": "signal-out",
        "targetHandle": "data"
      },
      {
        "source": "json-parse",
        "sourceHandle": "data",
        "target": "apply-state",
        "targetHandle": "changes"
      }
    ]
  }
}
